Subject: [PATCH] feat(ops): consolidated VPS go-live bootstrap for all four
 stacks

Add bootstrap_consolidated_vps_go_live.sh to install/sync football, racing,
trading shadow soak, and local FVE Docker on one box. Add install_fve_lines_stack.sh,
default FVE upstream to localhost when stack.env says 127.0.0.1, and detect local
/opt/fve when stack.env is missing.
